data.description: Just in time for Summer, this Stonecrest home is ready to be yours! Located in a beautiful neighborhood, this 3 bed, 2 bath home has plenty to offer. Enjoy family and friends in the spacious living room with an open concept. The adjoining kitchen offers nice countertops with an eat-in breakfast nook surrounded by beautiful windows offering plenty of natural light.  This home offers a new roof and a new outside A/C unit. This property is a must see for you to put your finishing touches on. Property being sold As-Is. Note: All information provided is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed and should be independently verified.
